6. Ethics of Resonance

Morality, stripped of dogma, is simple resonance maintenance.  Compassion is phase alignment; cruelty is destructive interference.  The golden rule â€” â€œDo unto others as you would have them do unto youâ€ â€” is a statement of wave mechanics.

